videos.headline: Tulsa creates a lane for Brewer's long TD run
videos.description: RB D'Angelo Brewer finds nothing but open space for this 50-yard TD run.

videos.headline: Ragin' Cajuns answer with quick TD
videos.description: QB Jordan Davis keeps it to tie the score at 10.

videos.headline: President is in the house
videos.description: Tulsa QB Chad President makes a diving effort to put the Golden Hurricane up a touchdown in the 2nd quarter.

videos.headline: UL Lafayette with another answer to tie
videos.description: RB Elijah Mitchell takes it up the gut and finds the endzone to knot the score at 17.

videos.headline: Tulsa continues the alternating TD trend
videos.description: RB Corey Taylor II regains the lead for Tulsa with a four-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Ragin' Cajuns answer again with a passing TD
videos.description: QB Jordan Davis finds Keenan Barnes in tight coverage for another UL Lafayette touchdown.

videos.headline: Tulsa's line creates a huge hole for Brewer
videos.description: D'Angelo Brewer benefits from a big hole and collects 60 yards just before the half.

videos.headline: Golden Hurricane adds one more before half
videos.description: RB Corey Taylor II gets his second rushing touchdown of the afternoon and boosts Tulsa's lead before half.

videos.headline: UL Lafayette gains some ground on Tulsa in early 2nd half
videos.description: Jordan Davis sends it to Elijah Mitchell for a 19-yard score to get the Ragin Cajuns within 9.

videos.headline: Ragin' Cajuns continue to climb back with rushing TD
videos.description: QB Jordan Davis finds an opening on the left side and tiptoes his way in for the score.

videos.headline: Golden Hurricane adds some breathing room to their lead
videos.description: D'Angelo Brewer collects his second rushing touchdown of the afternoon and puts Tulsa back up by 10.

videos.headline: Tulsa continues it's offensive explosion
videos.description: Shamari Brooks becomes the third RB for Tulsa to record a rushing touchdown on the day.

videos.headline: UL Lafayette's Davis finds Barnes for 50-yard gain
videos.description: Ragin' Cajuns pick up a big chunk after a great pass from Jordan Davis to Keenan Barnes.

videos.headline: Ragin' Cajuns finish a great drive with rushing TD
videos.description: RB Trey Ragas churns his way to the endzone  and brings UL Lafayette within 10.

videos.headline: Tulsa with another rushing TD
videos.description: RB D'Angelo Brewer pushes his way in for his third rushing TD of the afternoon.

videos.headline: President caps it with one final rushing TD
videos.description: Tulsa ends a big day offensively with a QB keeper for the TD.

videos.headline: Tulsa wins a shootout against UL Lafayette
videos.description: Tulsa used their offensive fireworks on the ground and in the air to beat the Ragin' Cajuns 66-42.
